title: Queen Discography @ 320Kbps
description:
Queen Discography
MP3 format @ 320Kbps

I used a Discography of Queen @ 320Kbps I had already, but it lacked organization and a few albums, so I added them and renamed the files, etc.
The ID3 tags are all pretty and organized and I added all the artwork.
